However, it’s important to note that while we strive for complete accuracy in all our translations, we cannot guarantee that they are 100% accurate, particularly when it comes to legal content. Consequently, the English version of this Privacy Policy is considered the original and prevailing version in the event of any discrepancy with the translated versions. The latest version of this Privacy Policy is always available in English on our website.1. Our Commitment to Data Privacy
