We acknowledge the enormous responsibility of safeguarding the private data you entrust us with. That’s why we’re constantly striving to meet the highest standards of privacy and security. Your data protection is embedded in everything we do.
Being a health company focused on female health, we recognize the paramount importance of privacy to our users:
As a UK company, we’re not required to have to comply with US criminal subpoenas requesting disclosure of data.
Also, we do not and will not sell any personal data.
We believe in transparency, and it’s paramount to us that you understand how your data is managed. We urge you to thoroughly read this Privacy Policy to understand how we manage your data. If you have any queries, don’t hesitate to contact us at
